entries.femaleVariant: Nah, couldn'ta been a sailfish. A real, live sailfish? Here? Come on.
Sure was fast enough. Goin' over sixty. Plus it had that fin, like in the pics.
Nah, girl. Musta been a drone. Or a torpedo.
No way. What they got shootin' torpedos in the Del Coronado?
Listen to those podcasts I sent you, then we'll talk.
Whole bay is teemin' with Militech submarines.
Man, rather it was one badass sailfish cruisin' in that sludge.
